01:04:56,765 --> 01:04:59,632
[Grimsby] A-And she is lovely.

934
01:04:59,701 --> 01:05:02,135
Congratulations, my dear.

935
01:05:02,204 --> 01:05:05,071
[Eric] We wish to be married
as soon as possible.

936
01:05:05,140 --> 01:05:09,167
[Grimsby] Oh, yes, of course, Eric, but,
uh, these things do take time, you know.

937
01:05:09,244 --> 01:05:12,941
This afternoon, Grimsby.
The wedding ship departs at sunset.

938
01:05:13,015 --> 01:05:18,043
Oh. Oh. Very well, Eric,
uh, as you wish.

939
01:05:23,458 --> 01:05:25,449
[snickers]

940
01:05:28,497 --> 01:05:30,488
[organ plays]

941
01:05:33,135 --> 01:05:36,662
[chatter, laughter]

942
01:05:49,017 --> 01:05:50,951
[cries]

943
01:06:12,174 --> 01:06:14,938
[hums: <i>The Wedding March]</i>

944
01:06:15,010 --> 01:06:18,138
[Ariel's voice] # <i>What a lovely</i>
<i>little bride I'll make</i>

945
01:06:18,213 --> 01:06:21,148
# <i>My dear, I'll look divine</i>

946
01:06:21,216 --> 01:06:22,808
[laughs]

947
01:06:22,884 --> 01:06:24,181
# <i>Things are working out</i>

948
01:06:24,252 --> 01:06:28,120
# <i>According to my ultimate design</i>

949
01:06:28,190 --> 01:06:29,782
[laughs]

950
01:06:29,858 --> 01:06:32,622
# <i>Soon I'll have that little mermaid</i>

951
01:06:32,694 --> 01:06:36,494
# <i>And the ocean will be mine</i> #

952
01:06:37,766 --> 01:06:40,132
[cackles]

953
01:06:40,202 --> 01:06:45,003
The sea witch! Oh, no!
She's gonna... I gotta...

954
01:06:45,073 --> 01:06:47,405
Ariel!

955
01:06:47,476 --> 01:06:50,570
Ariel!

956
01:06:50,646 --> 01:06:55,106
Ariel, I was flying...
Of course, I was flying. And...

957
01:06:55,183 --> 01:06:59,847
I saw the... the watch...
The witch was watching the mirror,

958
01:06:59,921 --> 01:07:03,584
and she was singin'
with a stolen set of pipes.

959
01:07:03,659 --> 01:07:06,423
Do you hear what I'm tellin' you?

960
01:07:06,495 --> 01:07:11,831
The prince is marrying
the sea witch in disguise!

961
01:07:11,900 --> 01:07:15,165
- Are you sure about this?
- Have I ever been wrong?

962
01:07:15,237 --> 01:07:17,228
I mean, when it's important?

963
01:07:17,305 --> 01:07:19,796
What are we gonna do?

964
01:07:19,875 --> 01:07:23,606
<i>[Ursula's voice] Before the sun</i>
<i>sets on the third day.</i>

965
01:07:23,679 --> 01:07:26,045
<i>[echoes] Day...</i>

966
01:07:30,419 --> 01:07:32,887
Ariel, grab onto that.

967
01:07:32,954 --> 01:07:36,788
Flounder, get her to that boat
as fast as your fins can carry you.

968
01:07:36,858 --> 01:07:38,826
I'll try!

969
01:07:38,894 --> 01:07:41,488
I gotta get to the sea king.
He must know about this.

970
01:07:41,563 --> 01:07:43,622
- What about me? What about me?
- You!

971
01:07:43,699 --> 01:07:47,066
Find a way to stall that wedding!

972
01:07:47,135 --> 01:07:49,069
Stall the wedding. W-What am I?

973
01:07:49,137 --> 01:07:51,901
What? That's it! [squawks]

974
01:07:51,973 --> 01:07:57,570
- [squawks]
- [chirping]

975
01:07:57,646 --> 01:08:01,241
[squawks]

976
01:08:01,316 --> 01:08:02,840
- [chattering]
- Let's go!

977
01:08:02,918 --> 01:08:05,580
We got an emergency here.

978
01:08:05,654 --> 01:08:08,088
[squawking, chirping]

979
01:08:08,156 --> 01:08:10,750
[organ plays]

980
01:08:10,826 --> 01:08:12,817
[Max growls]

981
01:08:14,162 --> 01:08:15,754
[yelps]

982
01:08:17,566 --> 01:08:19,534
Dearly beloved...

983
01:08:19,601 --> 01:08:24,937
[pants] Don't worry, Ariel.
We're gonna make it.

984
01:08:25,006 --> 01:08:26,940
We're almost there.

985
01:08:27,008 --> 01:08:30,910
Yes, um, do you, Eric, take Vanessa...

986
01:08:30,979 --> 01:08:34,210
to be your lawfully wedded wife

987
01:08:34,282 --> 01:08:36,876
for as long as you both shall live?

988
01:08:36,952 --> 01:08:39,147
I do.

989
01:08:39,221 --> 01:08:41,212
It being... And do you...

990
01:08:41,289 --> 01:08:43,757
[squawking, chirping]

991
01:08:45,193 --> 01:08:47,559
[gasps]

992
01:08:48,330 --> 01:08:50,230
- [screams]
- [barks]

993
01:08:50,298 --> 01:08:51,560
Oh!

994
01:08:51,633 --> 01:08:53,567
[seals bark]

995
01:08:53,635 --> 01:08:56,297
Oh! Oh! Oh!

996
01:08:56,404 --> 01:08:58,872
[screams]

997
01:08:59,875 --> 01:09:01,274
Then by the power...

998
01:09:01,343 --> 01:09:03,436
[Ursula's voice] Get away, you slimy...

999
01:09:03,512 --> 01:09:05,104
- Oh!
- [barks]

1000
01:09:08,517 --> 01:09:11,179
- [barks]
- Oh!

1001
01:09:12,587 --> 01:09:16,523
- Oh!
- [chattering]

1002
01:09:16,591 --> 01:09:19,059
- [squawks]
- Oh, why, you little...

1003
01:09:19,127 --> 01:09:22,563
[barks]

1004
01:09:22,631 --> 01:09:24,690
- [growls]
- [screams]

1005
01:09:27,803 --> 01:09:30,601
[Ariel's voice vocalizing]

1006
01:09:30,672 --> 01:09:32,264
[moans] Huh?

1007
01:09:32,340 --> 01:09:36,333
[Ariel's voice vocalizing]

1008
01:09:36,411 --> 01:09:39,847
[vocalizes]

1009
01:09:39,915 --> 01:09:41,940
Ariel?

1010
01:09:42,017 --> 01:09:45,248
- Eric.
- [barks]

1011
01:09:45,320 --> 01:09:47,413
You... You can talk?

1012
01:09:47,489 --> 01:09:51,448
- You're the one.
- Eric, get away from her.

1013
01:09:51,526 --> 01:09:55,292
- It was you all the time.
- Eric, I wanted to tell you.

1014
01:09:55,363 --> 01:09:59,493
- [Ursula] Eric, no!
- [moans]

1015
01:09:59,568 --> 01:10:02,503
You're too late! [cackles]

1016
01:10:02,571 --> 01:10:05,199
You're too late!

1017
01:10:08,109 --> 01:10:10,873
- [all gasp]
- [cackles]

1018
01:10:10,946 --> 01:10:15,212
- [gasps]
- So long, lover boy.

1019
01:10:15,283 --> 01:10:17,979
- Ariel!
- Poor little princess.

1020
01:10:18,053 --> 01:10:20,988
It's not you I'm after.
I've a much bigger fish to...

1021
01:10:21,056 --> 01:10:24,355
- Ursula, stop!
- Hmph!

1022
01:10:24,426 --> 01:10:29,728
Why, King Triton!
[chuckles] How are you?

1023
01:10:29,798 --> 01:10:33,359
- Let her go!
- Not a chance! She's mine now!

1024
01:10:33,435 --> 01:10:36,632
- We made a deal.
- Daddy, I'm sorry! I-I...

1025
01:10:36,705 --> 01:10:40,141
I didn't mean to! I didn't know!

1026
01:10:40,208 --> 01:10:43,507
[Ursula laughs]

1027
01:10:43,578 --> 01:10:44,875
You see?

1028
01:10:44,946 --> 01:10:48,279
The contract's legal, binding
and completely unbreakable,

1029
01:10:48,350 --> 01:10:50,341
even for you.

1030
01:10:50,418 --> 01:10:55,879
Of course, I always was a girl
with an eye for a bargain.

1031
01:10:55,957 --> 01:11:01,327
The daughter of the great sea king
is a very precious commodity.

1032
01:11:01,396 --> 01:11:05,594
But I might be willing
to make an exchange

1033
01:11:05,667 --> 01:11:09,603
for someone even better.

1034
01:11:09,671 --> 01:11:11,434
Eric, what are you doing?

1035
01:11:11,506 --> 01:11:15,203
Grim, I lost her once.
I'm not gonna lose her again!

1036
01:11:15,277 --> 01:11:19,873
Now, do we have a deal?

1037
01:11:22,417 --> 01:11:25,511
Ha! It's done then!

1038
01:11:27,489 --> 01:11:30,617
- [Ursula laughs]
- No! Oh, no!

1039
01:11:39,134 --> 01:11:41,261
Your Majesty.

1040
01:11:41,336 --> 01:11:42,598
Daddy.

1041
01:11:42,671 --> 01:11:47,165
- At last... it's mine.
- No.

1042
01:11:49,377 --> 01:11:53,643
- [cackles]
- You!

1043
01:11:53,715 --> 01:11:54,909
You monster!

1044
01:11:55,016 --> 01:11:57,177
Don't fool with me, ya little brat!

1045
01:11:57,218 --> 01:12:00,153
Contract or no, I'll blast... Ow!

1046
01:12:00,221 --> 01:12:02,815
- Why, you little fool.
- Eric! Eric, look out!

1047
01:12:02,891 --> 01:12:04,825
After him!

1048
01:12:07,228 --> 01:12:09,856
[pants]

1049
01:12:11,433 --> 01:12:14,334
Come on!

1050
01:12:14,402 --> 01:12:17,166
Ow!

1051
01:12:18,640 --> 01:12:21,939
Say goodbye to your sweetheart.

1052
01:12:22,010 --> 01:12:23,875
[shrieks]

1053
01:12:24,512 --> 01:12:26,605
[both scream]

1054
01:12:26,681 --> 01:12:31,414
Babies! My poor little poopsies.

1055
01:12:31,486 --> 01:12:34,011
[growls]

1056
01:12:41,429 --> 01:12:44,193
Eric, you've gotta get away from here.

1057
01:12:44,265 --> 01:12:46,529
No, I won't leave you.

1058
01:12:49,170 --> 01:12:51,161
[cackles]

1059
01:12:59,748 --> 01:13:04,014
[guttural laughter]

1060
01:13:04,085 --> 01:13:08,954
You pitiful, insignificant fools!

1061
01:13:09,024 --> 01:13:10,992
Look out!

1062
01:13:12,727 --> 01:13:15,696
Now I am the ruler of all the ocean!

1063
01:13:15,764 --> 01:13:19,393
The waves obey my every whim!

1064
01:13:19,467 --> 01:13:23,563
- Eric!
- [Eric screams]

1065
01:13:23,638 --> 01:13:29,338
The sea and all its spoils
bow to my power!

1066
01:13:48,096 --> 01:13:50,656
Eric!

1067
01:13:52,801 --> 01:13:55,668
[pants]

1068
01:14:13,254 --> 01:14:15,188
Oh! Oh!

1069
01:14:21,796 --> 01:14:24,560
[Ursula cackles]

1070
01:14:24,632 --> 01:14:27,726
So much for true love!

1071
01:14:32,440 --> 01:14:34,908
[screams]

1072
01:14:57,832 --> 01:15:00,699
[all moan]

1073
01:15:02,837 --> 01:15:04,395
[murmuring]

1074
01:15:25,193 --> 01:15:29,254
She really does love him,
doesn't she, Sebastian?

1075
01:15:29,330 --> 01:15:35,235
Mmm. Well, it's like
I always say, Your Majesty,

1076
01:15:35,303 --> 01:15:40,263
children got to be free
to lead their own lives.

1077
01:15:40,341 --> 01:15:42,275
You always say that?

1078
01:15:42,343 --> 01:15:45,107
[chuckles]

1079
01:15:45,180 --> 01:15:49,480
[sighs] Then I guess
there's just one problem left.

1080
01:15:49,551 --> 01:15:51,678
And what's that, Your Majesty?

1081
01:15:51,753 --> 01:15:55,382
How much I'm going to miss her.

1082
01:16:26,421 --> 01:16:28,321
[cheering]

1083
01:16:54,249 --> 01:16:56,615
[chef] Ah-ha!

1084
01:16:56,684 --> 01:16:59,346
[chef shouts]

1085
01:17:04,325 --> 01:17:08,386
[laughs] Yes!

1086
01:17:08,463 --> 01:17:10,363
Thank you. Thank you.

1087
01:17:20,308 --> 01:17:21,969
[whispers] I love you, Daddy.

1088
01:17:22,043 --> 01:17:26,377
[chorus] # <i>Now we can walk</i>
<i>Now we can run</i>

1089
01:17:26,447 --> 01:17:31,817
# <i>Now we can stay all day in the sun</i>

1090
01:17:33,021 --> 01:17:37,458
# <i>Just you and me</i>

1091
01:17:37,525 --> 01:17:41,928
# <i>And I can be</i>

1092
01:17:41,996 --> 01:17:48,595
# <i>Part of your world</i>

1093
01:17:48,670 --> 01:17:50,661
[chorus vocalizes]



